a at these points. In particular, it is\nproved that Kapranov's exceptional collection appears at points of the small\nquantum cohomology only for Grassmannians of small dimension (namely, less or\nequal than 2). Finally, a property of quasi-periodicity of the Stokes matrices\nof complex Grassmannians, along the locus of the small quantum cohomology, is\ndescribed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Nov 2018 16:49:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 May 2019 12:43:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-09"}
