e requirements\nnecessary for future improvements to reach the DFSZ axion model band are\ndiscussed in the paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Nov 2018 03:02:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Dec 2018 06:34:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 29 Mar 2019 05:34:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-02"}
