hifted or straightly undefined, our results\nindicate that is remarkably connected to the haloes angular momentum growth.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Nov 2018 14:17:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Mar 2019 17:53:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-14"}
